<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;CAHIER DE FONTENET&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONTRIBUTION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cahier de Fontenet is a citizen consultation document where opinions and grievances regarding political and financial matters are expressed."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"CAHIER DE FONTENET"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FEMME&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CITOYEN"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Femme is the contributor of the document, expressing her opinions and proposals related to public policies and reforms."&lt;SEP&gt;"Femme refers to the contributor of the text, who expresses opinions and grievances as a citizen."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"FEMME"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C2"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RÉDUCTION DES RETRAITES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Réduction des retraites proposes a significant reduction of pensions for former presidents and politicians to alleviate financial burdens."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"RÉDUCTION DES RETRAITES"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUPER-PRÉSIDENTE DE CROATIE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTEURINSTITUTIONNEL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Super-présidente de Croatie is hinted as a role model for reducing lavish governmental spending in France, especially at the Élysée and in ministries."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"SUPER-PRÉSIDENTE DE CROATIE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ISF&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TYPEIMPOT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"ISF (Impôt de Solidarity sur la Fortune) refers to the wealth tax that the contributor suggests reinstating for the wealthier population."&lt;SEP&gt;"ISF (Impôt de Solidarité sur la Fortune) is a wealth tax in France that has been abolished, leading to grievances regarding fiscal injustice."&lt;SEP&gt;"ISF refers to the proposed reinstatement of the Impôt de Solidarité sur la Fortune, a wealth tax seen as a corrective measure for fiscal inequality."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-e5637c5257ccf7da22163a78a1b7f116</data>
  <data key="d3">"ISF"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C3"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DIALOGUE AVEC LE PEUPLE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Dialogue avec le peuple refers to accepting public discourse and listening to citizens as an essential approach for governance."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"DIALOGUE AVEC LE PEUPLE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RÉFÉRENDUM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"QUESTION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Référendum is raised as a method for engaging with citizens and obtaining their opinions on significant issues."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"RÉFÉRENDUM"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PAIX ET SÉRÉNITÉ&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONSENSUS"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Paix et sérénité represent the desired states of society that the contributor hopes will be restored through political listening and reforms."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"PAIX ET SÉRÉNITÉ"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C0"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CAHIER DE DOLÉANCES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONSULTATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cahier de doléances is a document meant for gathering citizen grievances and opinions regarding public policies and governance."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"CAHIER DE DOLÉANCES"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MAIRE DE FONTENET&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTEURINSTITUTIONNEL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Maire de Fontenet is the recipient of the contribution, representing the local government and authority responsible for addressing the concerns raised by citizens."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"MAIRE DE FONTENET"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;GUERRE CIVILE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Guerre civile refers to the contributor's expressed anger about the societal unrest and challenges faced by the citizens in their country."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"GUERRE CIVILE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FONDS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"QUESTION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Fonds indicates a query about where to find financial resources to support public services and initiatives."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"FONDS"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TRAIN DE VIE À L’ÉLYSÉE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Train de vie à l’Élysée refers to the proposed reduction of the extravagant lifestyle and expenses of the government, particularly at the presidential level."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"TRAIN DE VIE À L’ÉLYSÉE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;POTS CASSÉS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"METAPHOR"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Pots cassés is a metaphor used to express the idea that the same group of citizens always suffers the consequences of political mismanagement and crisis."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"POTS CASSÉS"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C1"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BEAU PAYS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Beau pays is a conceptual expression reflecting the contributor's love for France and desire to restore its image through effective governance."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d3">"BEAU PAYS"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C2"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LIBERTÉ, ÉGALITÉ ET FRATERNITÉ&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"This phrase inscribed on public buildings symbolizes the fundamental values of the French Republic. The contribution questions its current relevance."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"LIBERTÉ, ÉGALITÉ ET FRATERNITÉ"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CITOYENS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CITOYEN"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Citizens are individuals contributing their thoughts on societal issues affecting their living conditions and the responsibilities of elected officials."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"CITOYENS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;C.D.I.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TYPEREPONDANT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"C.D.I. refers to a permanent employment contract, representing job stability which is problematic when citizens cannot afford living expenses."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"C.D.I."</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LOGEMENTS SOCIAUX&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"SERVICEPUBLIC"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Social housing is a public service that aims to provide affordable housing. The contribution criticizes the refusal to construct more housing."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"LOGEMENTS SOCIAUX"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;AGRICULTEURS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTEURINSTITUTIONNEL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Farmers face the challenge of selling products below cost, which threatens their livelihood and contradicts the values of fair work."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"AGRICULTEURS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CAHIERS DE DOLÉANCES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONTRIBUTION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cahiers de doléances are citizen contributions that reflect grievances and opinions regarding current injustices and public policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Les cahiers de doléances sont des documents permettant aux citoyens d'exprimer leurs opinions, propositions et doléances."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-3fdff2f5c96bbef929428424fa8d0d1b&lt;SEP&gt;contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"CAHIERS DE DOLÉANCES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ÉLUS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTEURINSTITUTIONNEL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Elected officials are representatives criticized for their privileges and lack of engagement with the concerns of average citizens."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"ÉLUS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PRIVILEGES ANCIENS ÉLUS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Former elected officials retain privileges which are viewed as unfair, given their lack of responsibility towards their previous duties."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"PRIVILEGES ANCIENS ÉLUS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TAXES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The contribution expresses grievances regarding increasing taxes viewed as burdensome for the general populace to remedy the financial mismanagement."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"TAXES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;1789&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONSENSUS"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Referencing the year 1789 signifies the historical abolition of privileges which the contributor feels is being undone in modern society."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"1789"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HOMME&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CITOYEN"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Homme refers to a male citizen contributing to the grievances expressed in the document, highlighting issues faced by individuals working in various sectors."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"HOMME"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;AMENDES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Fines are mentioned as a preferred choice by some cities over taking action to build social housing, representing systemic issues in public policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"AMENDES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PRODUITS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Products sold by farmers at a loss are a theme representing the economic challenges facing the agricultural sector."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"PRODUITS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CUMUL DES MANDATS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The accumulation of mandates refers to elected representatives holding multiple positions which may lead to conflicts of interest and detachment from constituents."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"CUMUL DES MANDATS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INDEMNITÉS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Indemnities received by elected officials are viewed as excessive, especially during times when citizens struggle financially."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"INDEMNITÉS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HONTE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OPINION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"‘Honte’ expresses a strong opinion regarding the actions and decisions of cities that opt to pay fines instead of addressing housing shortages."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"HONTE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PETIT PEUPLE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONSENSUS"</data>
  <data key="d1">"‘Petit Peuple’ refers to ordinary citizens, emphasizing their struggles against the elite and their financial burdens."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"PETIT PEUPLE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DÉFICITS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Deficits are mentioned in the context of increasing taxes that the citizens feel are unjust, used to support a few privileged individuals."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"DÉFICITS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PRÉROGATIVES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Prerogatives are discussed concerning former elected officials who still enjoy benefits without holding any power, highlighting inequities in public service."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"PRÉROGATIVES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;GENDARMES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTEURINSTITUTIONNEL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Gendarmes are referenced as public officials tasked with protecting properties of former elected officials, raising concerns about resource allocation."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d3">"GENDARMES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;GILETS JAUNES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"COURANTIDEOLOGIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Gilets Jaunes is a social movement in France advocating for various grievances related to economic injustices, including taxes and living standards."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"GILETS JAUNES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DOLÉANCES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Doléances refers to grievances expressed by citizens, particularly related to taxes, cost of living, and retirement benefits."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"DOLÉANCES"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;IMPÔT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TYPEIMPOT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Impôt refers to taxes that citizens are required to pay based on their income, which is a central theme in the opinion expressed by the citizen."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"IMPÔT"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RÉFÉRENDUM D’INITIATIVE CITOYEN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"REFORMEDEMOCRATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Référendum d’Initiative Citoyen is a proposed democratic reform aimed at allowing citizens to have a stronger voice in political decisions."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"RÉFÉRENDUM D’INITIATIVE CITOYEN"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CANTINE GRATUITE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PROPOSITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cantine Gratuite is a proposal suggesting that school meals should be free for all children, ensuring they have access to balanced food."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"CANTINE GRATUITE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TERRITOIRE FRANÇAIS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TERRITOIRE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Territoire Français refers to the geographical area of France where the citizen’s opinions and proposals regarding taxation and policies are concerned."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"TERRITOIRE FRANÇAIS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ASSISTANAT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Assistanat refers to social assistance programs which the contributor critiques, advocating for a more equitable system of taxation instead."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"ASSISTANAT"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;NIVEAU DE VIE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Niveau de vie refers to the standard of living, a key concern mentioned in the context of grievances about economic conditions."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"NIVEAU DE VIE"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C2"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RETRAITES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Retraites refers to pension benefits that are mentioned as being negatively impacted, highlighting concerns of the elderly."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"RETRAITES"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C2"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PROMESSES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Promesses refers to the unfulfilled promises made by elected officials, which the contributor criticizes as a recurring issue."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"PROMESSES"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C2"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ÉGALITÉ EN DROITS ET EN DEVOIRS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONSENSUS"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Égalité en droits et en devoirs is a principle emphasized in the text, advocating for equal rights and responsibilities for all citizens."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"ÉGALITÉ EN DROITS ET EN DEVOIRS"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SCOLARISATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"THEMATIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Scolarisation refers to the education system in which free meals through Cantine Gratuite would benefit children."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d3">"SCOLARISATION"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EMMANUEL MACRON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTEURINSTITUTIONNEL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Emmanuel Macron is the President of France, whose policies are being critiqued by citizens in terms of fiscal measures benefiting the wealthy."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e5637c5257ccf7da22163a78a1b7f116</data>
  <data key="d3">"EMMANUEL MACRON"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C3"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CSG&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TYPEIMPOT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"CSG (Contributions Sociales Généralisées) is a social contribution tax that has increased, affecting lower-income citizens adversely."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e5637c5257ccf7da22163a78a1b7f116</data>
  <data key="d3">"CSG"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C3"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;APL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"SERVICEPUBLIC"</data>
  <data key="d1">"APL (Aide Personnalisée au Logement) is a housing subsidy whose reduction has been criticized for worsening living conditions."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e5637c5257ccf7da22163a78a1b7f116</data>
  <data key="d3">"APL"</data>
  <data key="d4">[{"level": 0, "cluster": "L0C3"}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"MESUREECOLOGIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"CICE (Crédit d'Impôt pour la Compétitivité et l'Emploi) is a tax measure that is believed to benefit corporations without proving effectiveness."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e5637c5257ccf7da22163a78a1b7f116</data>
  <data key="d3">"CICE"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;GAFA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ACTEURINSTITUTIONNEL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"GAFA refers to major multinational technology companies like Google, Amazon, Facebook, and Apple, which are subjects of taxation proposals."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e5637c5257ccf7da22163a78a1b7f116</data>
  <data key="d3">"GAFA"</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DISCRIMINATION FISCALE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOLEANCE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Discrimination fiscale is a grievance regarding the unfair tax burden on lower-income individuals compared to wealthier taxpayers."</data>
  <data key="d2">contrib-e5637c5257ccf7da22163a78a1b7f116</data>
