  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CAHIER DE DOLÉANCES&quot;" target="&quot;FONDS&quot;">
  <data key="d5">7.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"Cahier de doléances questions the availability of Fonds as part of expressing public grievances and seeking financial relief."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CAHIER DE DOLÉANCES&quot;" target="&quot;TRAIN DE VIE À L’ÉLYSÉE&quot;">
  <data key="d5">8.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The mention of Train de vie à l’Élysée reveals a direct relationship with the contributor's suggestions for reducing governmental expenses."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CAHIER DE DOLÉANCES&quot;" target="&quot;POTS CASSÉS&quot;">
  <data key="d5">9.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The term Pots cassés reflects the idea that the outcomes of political failures disproportionately affect ordinary citizens, as stated in the Cahier de doléances."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-605c676244d35c4cbb487b9c47cad602</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LIBERTÉ, ÉGALITÉ ET FRATERNITÉ&quot;" target="&quot;CITOYENS&quot;">
  <data key="d5">9.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The phrase symbolizes citizens' expectations from their elected officials, which they feel are not being met in current circumstances."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CITOYENS&quot;" target="&quot;LOGEMENTS SOCIAUX&quot;">
  <data key="d5">8.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The citizens express grievances regarding the lack of social housing, which affects their ability to live comfortably."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CITOYENS&quot;" target="&quot;ÉLUS&quot;">
  <data key="d5">9.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The elected officials are criticized by citizens for their detachment from the realities faced by the population."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CITOYENS&quot;" target="&quot;C.D.I.&quot;">
  <data key="d5">7.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"Citizens in C.D.I. jobs are highlighted as struggling to afford living, indicating that employment alone does not guarantee a decent life."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CITOYENS&quot;" target="&quot;TAXES&quot;">
  <data key="d5">8.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"Increasing taxes are a direct grievance to citizens, who feel overburdened and exploited by the current financial system."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LOGEMENTS SOCIAUX&quot;" target="&quot;AGRICULTEURS&quot;">
  <data key="d5">6.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The plight of farmers selling below cost is mentioned alongside the issue of housing, indicating a broader economic concern affecting multiple groups."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LOGEMENTS SOCIAUX&quot;" target="&quot;CAHIERS DE DOLÉANCES&quot;">
  <data key="d5">8.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The contribution source discusses social housing as a key issue, indicating its importance in citizen dissatisfaction."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CAHIERS DE DOLÉANCES&quot;" target="&quot;HABITANTE D’UNE COMMUNE RURALE&quot;">
  <data key="d5">9.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"L'habitante utilise les cahiers de doléances pour exprimer ses préoccupations et propositions en tant que citoyenne."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-3fdff2f5c96bbef929428424fa8d0d1b</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CAHIERS DE DOLÉANCES&quot;" target="&quot;PRÉNOM NOM&quot;">
  <data key="d5">6.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"Le nom inséré par l'habitante témoigne de son engagement dans le processus de consultation via les cahiers de doléances."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-3fdff2f5c96bbef929428424fa8d0d1b</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ÉLUS&quot;" target="&quot;PRIVILEGES ANCIENS ÉLUS&quot;">
  <data key="d5">7.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The contribution points out that former elected officials maintain privileges that are no longer deserved, indicating a lack of accountability."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TAXES&quot;" target="&quot;1789&quot;">
  <data key="d5">6.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The reference to 1789 suggests that the modern tax situation is reminiscent of historical inequalities, creating a sense of urgency and frustration."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-719920efaf004bc78c2db5900ff5f1bf</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GILETS JAUNES&quot;" target="&quot;DOLÉANCES&quot;">
  <data key="d5">8.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The Gilets Jaunes movement expresses Doléances regarding economic issues, taxes, and living conditions."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GILETS JAUNES&quot;" target="&quot;RÉFÉRENDUM D’INITIATIVE CITOYEN&quot;">
  <data key="d5">7.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The Gilets Jaunes movement calls for the Référendum d’Initiative Citoyen, aligning with their demand for greater citizen power."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;DOLÉANCES&quot;" target="&quot;IMPÔT&quot;">
  <data key="d5">7.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"Doléances highlight concerns regarding taxation levels and fairness, particularly how it impacts living standards."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;DOLÉANCES&quot;" target="&quot;RÉFÉRENDUM D’INITIATIVE CITOYEN&quot;">
  <data key="d5">9.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The concerns expressed in Doléances relate to a demand for the Référendum d’Initiative Citoyen, emphasizing citizen engagement in governance."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;DOLÉANCES&quot;" target="&quot;CANTINE GRATUITE&quot;">
  <data key="d5">8.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The proposal for Cantine Gratuite addresses Doléances related to economic hardship faced by families, ensuring basic needs are met."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;IMPÔT&quot;" target="&quot;TERRITOIRE FRANÇAIS&quot;">
  <data key="d5">7.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The Impôt is relevant to all individuals living in the Territoire Français, focusing on equitable taxation based on income."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;IMPÔT&quot;" target="&quot;ASSISTANAT&quot;">
  <data key="d5">6.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"Assistanat is criticized in relation to how it intersects with the system of Impôt, suggesting reform for fairness in taxation and assistance."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;IMPÔT&quot;" target="&quot;CANTINE GRATUITE&quot;">
  <data key="d5">7.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The proposal for Cantine Gratuite relates to funding that can be derived from a fairer tax system, specifically taxing the wealthy."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-43e9da3d3a1ee4123a56799ed5673e11</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;IMPÔT&quot;" target="&quot;FRAUDE FISCALE&quot;">
  <data key="d5">9.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The issue of fraud fiscale relates directly to concerns over the government's efficacy in tax collection and the fairness of the system."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-e5637c5257ccf7da22163a78a1b7f116</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EMMANUEL MACRON&quot;" target="&quot;CSG&quot;">
  <data key="d5">7.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The increase in CSG is a policy under Emmanuel Macron that is perceived negatively by citizens who face financial strain."</data>
  <data key="d7">contrib-e5637c5257ccf7da22163a78a1b7f116</data>
  <data key="d8">1</data>
  <data key="d9">RELATED_TO</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CSG&quot;" target="&quot;APL&quot;">
  <data key="d5">8.0</data>
  <data key="d6">"The reduction in APL is linked to the broader context of increased taxes like the CSG, impacting citizens' livelihoods."</data>
